snippet.title: BOBR KURWA - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now at ITCH.IO  BOBR KURWA | Free Early access
Steam release soon
BOBR KURWA is a roguelike top-down shooter where you control  3 unique heroes at once, each with distinct spells. Blast through the Polish forest, collecting powerful items and Upgrades.
